headline: Intel Stock Is a Speculative buy Because of This 1 Factor
summary: Although recovery prospects are uncertain, Intel continues to hold certain competitive advantages.  The decline of Intel (NASDAQ: INTC) and the numerous failed efforts to recover its leadership in the chip market have undoubtedly frustrated many investors.  The company has hired and dismissed several CEOs who have tried and failed to return Intel to competitiveness.
